          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-1-1644337905746-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>While the chips are cooking, peel and finely chop (or grate) your <strong>garlic</strong></p><p>Dice your <strong>apple[s] </strong>(skin on) finely and discard the <strong>core[s]</strong></p><p>Peel and finely chop your <strong>shallot[s]</strong></p><p>Chop your <strong>parsley </strong>finely, including the stalks</p>",
