    {
      "instruction": "<p>Heat a large, wide-based pan (preferably non-stick) with a generous drizzle of <strong>vegetable oil</strong> over a medium-high heat</p><p>Once hot, add the<strong> garlic panko chicken</strong> and cook for 5 min on each side, or until golden and cooked through (no pink meat!) – this is your <strong>crispy garlic chicken</strong></p><p>Tip: Cooking for 5? You may need to do this in batches!</p>",
